38fbd2f2-45fe-4f65-b425-3d3cd26fde0b.title: <player>
38fbd2f2-45fe-4f65-b425-3d3cd26fde0b.text:
Hi, you're free to go! Your kidnappers don't seem to be
about right now.

7c50435b-1932-4b7e-9239-da1ef4d5a8d1.title: Elena
7c50435b-1932-4b7e-9239-da1ef4d5a8d1.text:
Thank you, being kidnapped was so inconvenient. I was
on my way back to East Ardougne with some samples,
I want to see if I can diagnose a cure for this plague.

8185dc5a-63da-47f2-a6b1-1f75aeb4b8c0.title: <player>
8185dc5a-63da-47f2-a6b1-1f75aeb4b8c0.text:
Well you can leave via the manhole in the middle of the
city.

962821d9-5c56-4c45-9630-0019e9f74eb3.title: Elena
962821d9-5c56-4c45-9630-0019e9f74eb3.text:
Go and see my father, I'll make sure he adequately
rewards you. Now I'd better leave while I still can.

984e40a6-f228-4f04-a30d-ebd0a3335214.title: Note
984e40a6-f228-4f04-a30d-ebd0a3335214.text: Elena teleports out of cell and back home.

d859784d-9252-4168-bc09-95689168f4f7.title: Note
d859784d-9252-4168-bc09-95689168f4f7.text:
Cant talk to her until your in the cell with her..
place her in the back of the cell to reduce chances of exploit.

7a59aa88-c607-4603-bf89-435f2c73ad6c.title: Elena
7a59aa88-c607-4603-bf89-435f2c73ad6c.text: You too, thanks for freeing me.

4c9e9739-2a7a-4db7-9c44-a452127e5a0e.title: Elena
4c9e9739-2a7a-4db7-9c44-a452127e5a0e.text:
It's just a shame the mourners confiscated my
equipment.

2c12f04c-4d90-4af7-9dda-a4737b55a4cb.title: Elena
2c12f04c-4d90-4af7-9dda-a4737b55a4cb.text:
My distillator. I can't test any plague samples without
it. They're holding it in the Mourner Headquarters in
West Ardougne.

c04c1424-0cf2-4ed7-a895-d1feaaa69a3a.title: Elena
c04c1424-0cf2-4ed7-a895-d1feaaa69a3a.text:
I must somehow retrieve that distillator if I am to find
a cure for this awful affliction. Do you think you could
help me?

9902bd4d-314b-4384-a519-d3342f77c5c3.title: <player>
9902bd4d-314b-4384-a519-d3342f77c5c3.text: I'm busy at the moment, I'm afraid.
